//! Same-bare-name type fixture (wide layout). Exports a `Widget` record whose
//! sole field is an `i64`. Its sibling `hew::widgeti8` exports a `Widget` of the
//! same bare name with an `i8` field — a divergent layout. An importer that
//! constructs and reads both `Widget`s must resolve each through its
//! module-qualified identity; keying the MIR layout/field registry on the bare
//! name `Widget` collides across the two packages (last-write-wins).

pub type Widget {
    v: i64;
}
